Package: miRBaseVersions.db
Type: Package
Title: Collection of mature miRNA names of 23 different miRBase release versions
Version: 1.3.0
Authors@R: person("Stefan", "Haunsberger", email = "stefan.haunsberger@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Annotation package containing all available miRNA names from 23 versions (data from http://www.mirbase.org/). Releases 6.0 through 22.1; v22.1 is exposed as an alias of v22.0 because miRBase 22.1 only updated the high-confidence subset (which this package does not model).
License: Artistic-2.0
Imports: AnnotationDbi, DBI, RSQLite, methods, gtools
biocViews: Preprocessing, miRNA, AnnotationData
LazyData: TRUE
Suggests:
    testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    annotate
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
